DESCRIPTION:About SCORE Office Hours \nSCORE is the nation’s largest networ
	k of volunteer\, expert business mentors. Since 1964\, SCORE has helped mo
	re than 11 million entrepreneurs start\, grow\, or successfully exit a bus
	iness. SCORE’s 10\,000 volunteers provide free\, expert mentoring\, resour
	ces\, and education in all 50 U.S. states and territories. \nOffice Hours 
	with SCORE take place each Friday morning. Additional partners will be on-
	site the second Friday of each month (excluding holidays)\n\nhttps://iondi
	strict.com/event/score-office-hours-42/\n\nFrom Ion District
